   James meets Maggie, who is determined to decorate her 1930s house using 
   eco-paints, whilst restoring and reusing the original features.
   In Northampton, we meet Julie and her Dad, who with Dick&#039;s help, install 
   a solar panel on the roof. 
   We return to the Keenans on the Wirral. The guest wing of their big 
   eco-build is nearing completion. They get stuck in and learn how to use 
   environmentally friendly lime plaster.
